559
00:28:33,625 --> 00:28:34,120
Since you've had a nanny from the palace

560
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:35,800
to teach you a few things?

561
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,338
I am in no position to even teach you now.

562
00:28:37,338 --> 00:28:38,000
Very well!

563
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,520
Do it yourself then.

564
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:45,860
What's wrong?

565
00:28:48,800 --> 00:28:51,150
Sixth Miss' Aunt Wei is here.

566
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:59,160
