567
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:00,840
I personally made barbecued lamb for you,

568
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,200
you should have it all!

569
00:29:02,475 --> 00:29:03,315
Miss!

570
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,360
Hello, Madam.

571
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:08,560
I'm Miss' personal maid,

572
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,240
my name is Danju.

573
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:11,240
If Madam needs anything,

574
00:29:11,575 --> 00:29:14,095
please let me know.

575
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:16,725
Let me help you with your bag.

576
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,280
Let's go, Aunt.

577
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:24,560
Xiaotao, start the meal!

578
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:25,450
Alright.

579
00:29:43,325 --> 00:29:44,245
Just a moment.

580
00:30:28,975 --> 00:30:29,855
Aunt,

581
00:30:29,855 --> 00:30:31,455
we washed these ourselves.

582
00:30:31,455 --> 00:30:32,495
They're clean.

583
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:36,060
If it's just some dust,

584
00:30:36,650 --> 00:30:38,490
it doesn’t matter even if I ingest it.

585
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:43,400
But who knows what it might be?

586
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:49,050
Madam, what is this for?

587
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:01,400
Okay,

588
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:03,700
we can now drink wine

589
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:05,100
and eat with peace of mind.

590
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,630
Aunt, have some meat.

591
00:31:23,175 --> 00:31:24,735
Aunt, have some meat.

592
00:31:30,075 --> 00:31:30,955
I don't like light.

593
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:34,360
If it's extremely bright, I can't sleep.

594
00:31:34,375 --> 00:31:35,375
Tonight,

595
00:31:35,375 --> 00:31:36,975
put up some bed-curtains for me.

596
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:39,680
Yes. Madam,

597
00:31:40,050 --> 00:31:43,530
we have prepared a guest room for you.

598
00:31:45,525 --> 00:31:48,125
I'll sleep with Ming'er tonight.

599
00:31:51,275 --> 00:31:53,850
You eat too, have some more.

600
00:32:25,300 --> 00:32:26,620
Miss, good night.

601
00:32:27,225 --> 00:32:28,385
Madam, good night.

602
00:32:28,850 --> 00:32:30,170
I'm leaving now.

603
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,700
You may leave us.

604
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,225
Ming'er.

605
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,080
Ming'er, come here.

606
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:47,960
What is it, Aunt?

607
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,760
Come here now.

608
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:52,175
Aunt, what's wrong with you?

609
00:32:52,175 --> 00:32:53,935
Why are you so nervous?

610
00:32:54,560 --> 00:32:57,900
I just ran into Xiaodie a few days ago.

611
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,575
Who?

612
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,680
I was at Qionghua Taoist temple the other day,

613
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,160
to add incense oil for your Mother.

614
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:06,600
Coincidentally,

615
00:33:06,950 --> 00:33:10,390
I bumped into your mother's old maid, Xiaodie.

616
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:13,920
Sister Xiaodie? Xiaodie?

617
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:16,160
How is she?

618
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,880
Xiaodie told me that she dare

619
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:20,240
to swear before the Taoist Saints

620
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:23,160
that she never stole anything from your mother.

621
00:33:23,525 --> 00:33:26,245
Someone must have placed those items in her room.

622
00:33:28,475 --> 00:33:29,275
Who was it?

623
00:33:32,275 --> 00:33:33,275
She didn't say.

624
00:33:34,125 --> 00:33:36,165
She thought about it but couldn't figure it out.

625
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:38,120
Anyone is possible.

626
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,160
Child,

627
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:44,400
the Sheng family is like a bramble thicket.

628
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:46,560
You are all alone here.

629
00:33:47,075 --> 00:33:49,315
Heaven knows when someone might want to harm you!

630
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:53,240
Grandmother appointed all the people serving me.

631
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:54,590
They're all capable.

632
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,780
Aunt, don't worry.

633
00:33:57,800 --> 00:34:02,090
Aunt, who do you think wanted to frame her?

634
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:05,130
What benefit would the person gain?

635
00:34:06,275 --> 00:34:07,515
Coveting her position?

636
00:34:09,275 --> 00:34:10,035
No.

637
00:34:11,475 --> 00:34:15,395
Serving my mother was a thankless job.

638
00:34:16,275 --> 00:34:17,835
What benefit would the person get?

639
00:34:19,550 --> 00:34:21,550
It must have been maidservants and old nannies

640
00:34:21,550 --> 00:34:23,470
was fighting over positions and favors.

641
00:34:24,025 --> 00:34:25,465
It happened so long ago,

642
00:34:25,875 --> 00:34:26,915
how can we find it out?

643
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:29,460
Either way, there are too many intrigues in this house.

644
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:32,000
I'm worried about you.

645
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,560
That's why I'm here.

646
00:34:34,425 --> 00:34:36,345
Do not be careless or lower your guard.

647
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:38,160
When you eat in the future,

648
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,640
just do as what I did.

649
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,080
Test it with silver needles

650
00:34:41,375 --> 00:34:43,135
and rinse the wares with boiling water.

651
00:34:45,225 --> 00:34:46,985
You should be careful during the night as well.

652
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,200
You must check the items in your room

653
00:34:49,680 --> 00:34:51,520
every two to three days.

654
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:53,160
Check if you've lost anything,

655
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:54,375
but more importantly check that

656
00:34:54,650 --> 00:34:56,335
you don't have something extra.

657
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,225
Remember this.

658
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,000
I understand, Aunt.

659
00:35:04,475 --> 00:35:08,380
The person who framed her may still be in this house

660
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:11,240
or perhaps not anymore.

661
00:35:16,770 --> 00:35:18,770
Aunt.

662
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,280
Who could it be?

663
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:31,538
I picked this piece of meat

664
00:35:31,538 --> 00:35:33,075
in Butcher Zhang's store.

665
00:35:33,350 --> 00:35:37,950
It's good for both barbecuing or roasting.

666
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:40,640
Aunt has a good appetite.

667
00:35:40,975 --> 00:35:42,935
It even makes Grandmother's appetite better.

668
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:47,000
Greetings, Sixth Miss.

669
00:35:47,350 --> 00:35:48,030
Ms Zhou.

670
00:35:50,975 --> 00:35:54,175
Miss, are you going to personally cook dishes again?

671
00:35:54,775 --> 00:35:55,415
Yes.

672
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:58,650
I heard that your Aunt was here.

673
00:35:58,650 --> 00:36:00,050
Why haven't I seen her?

674
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:05,360
Aunt is from a farming family.

675
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,600
She's not very good at socializing

676
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:07,600
and doesn't go out much.

677
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:10,100
That's no good.

678
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:11,860
You must allow us to invite her to a meal.

679
00:36:12,570 --> 00:36:13,650
We dare not trouble you, Ms Zhou,

680
00:36:13,650 --> 00:36:14,890
we'll host her ourselves.

681
00:36:16,275 --> 00:36:17,955
It's just an extra pair of chopsticks.

682
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:20,080
Miss, if you don't mind,

683
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:21,320
come over tonight.

684
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:23,400
We can have the most popular "Icy Custard" banquet

685
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:26,120
in the capital these days with Mistress Lin.

686
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,600
Ms Zhou, can you make the decisions

687
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:29,400
for Mistress Lin now?

688
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,660
But it's so inopportune,

689
00:36:32,425 --> 00:36:35,025
my Aunt is going back to Yangzhou tomorrow.

690
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,840
Why such a rush?

691
00:36:40,250 --> 00:36:41,450
She should stay for a few more days

692
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:43,390
and have fun in Dongjing.

693
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,525
She should stay for a few more days.

694
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:48,240
She came to speak to me on some matters,

695
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,920
now that is done, naturally she'll head back.

696
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:51,740
Don't want things to go awry because of her late return.

697
00:36:54,450 --> 00:36:55,490
I understand.

698
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:15,280
That Madam Wei came from afar.

699
00:37:15,575 --> 00:37:16,695
I wonder what she said.

700
00:37:17,525 --> 00:37:19,725
It must be something fishy.

701
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:21,340
Watch her.

702
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:26,630
Incense burning can teach one tranquility and calm.

703
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:29,400
Flower arrangement can best sooth one's feelings

704
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,450
and temper their character.

705
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:33,325
In learning these skills,

706
00:37:34,450 --> 00:37:36,650
your bearing is only secondary.

707
00:37:37,325 --> 00:37:39,965
What's more valuable is cultivating your disposition.

708
00:37:41,855 --> 00:37:44,175
Beside you, you have

709
00:37:44,175 --> 00:37:46,375
the best quality calming incense.

710
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:49,510
If you control the fire well,

711
00:37:50,775 --> 00:37:54,175
a fingernail-sized piece can burn for four hours.

712
00:37:54,775 --> 00:37:56,855
The fragrance will last without dissipating.

713
00:38:02,700 --> 00:38:04,140
You may all start preparing it.

714
00:39:57,475 --> 00:40:00,150
Sister, could you have forgotten

715
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:01,550
to place the silver divider over the coal?

716
00:40:02,625 --> 00:40:04,625
The coal has burned the incense.

717
00:40:23,775 --> 00:40:24,855
Xiaodie told me that

718
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:27,880
she dared to swear before the Taoist Saints

719
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:30,400
that she did not steal anything from your mother.

720
00:40:30,775 --> 00:40:33,175
Someone must have placed those things in her room.

721
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,725
Nanny, I'm clumsy.

722
00:40:46,725 --> 00:40:48,550
I will be done soon.

723
00:40:50,875 --> 00:40:52,395
Sixth Sister, don't get anxious,

724
00:40:52,825 --> 00:40:56,385
this kind of thing requires focus and deft hands.

725
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,680
Those without the savvy

726
00:40:59,075 --> 00:41:01,675
will not be able to do it.

727
00:41:07,775 --> 00:41:09,120
Go away.
